properties.title: Modern Downtown Apartment
properties.description: Stunning modern apartment in the heart of downtown. Features floor-to-ceiling windows, hardwood floors, and top-of-the-line appliances. Walking distance to subway and major attractions.

properties.title: Charming Victorian House
properties.description: Beautiful Victorian-style house with original details preserved. Features a spacious garden, updated kitchen, and stunning city views. Perfect for families looking for character and charm.

properties.title: Luxury Beachfront Condo
properties.description: Breathtaking ocean views from this luxury beachfront condominium. Resort-style amenities including pool, gym, and spa. Modern finishes throughout with private balcony.

properties.title: Cozy Studio Apartment
properties.description: Perfect starter home or investment property. Compact yet functional studio in a vibrant neighborhood. Close to restaurants, cafes, and public transportation.

properties.title: Suburban Family Home
properties.description: Spacious family home in quiet suburban neighborhood. Large backyard perfect for entertaining, attached garage, and excellent school district. Move-in ready condition.

properties.title: Urban Loft Conversion
properties.description: Industrial chic loft in converted warehouse. High ceilings, exposed brick walls, and modern amenities. Located in trendy arts district with galleries and restaurants nearby.

properties.title: Mountain View Cabin
properties.description: Rustic cabin with modern updates and stunning mountain views. Perfect for outdoor enthusiasts. Features wood-burning fireplace, large deck, and easy access to hiking trails.

properties.title: Historic Brownstone
properties.description: Beautifully restored 19th-century brownstone in prestigious neighborhood. Original architectural details combined with modern conveniences. Private garden and parking space included.

properties.title: Penthouse Suite
properties.description: Luxury penthouse with panoramic city and water views. Floor-to-ceiling windows, private elevator access, and rooftop terrace. Premium building amenities and concierge service.

properties.title: Garden Apartment
properties.description: Ground-floor apartment with private garden access. Recently renovated with eco-friendly features. Great natural light and close to public transportation and bike paths.
